name: Jenny
description: Right now I’m Single married before and would be glad if i encounter a man of high caliber,good attitude,self respect and ambition,a man who knows what he wants and know how to get it, he has to be understanding and sincere that way a relationship would be smoother…I would like a man that will love and respect me for who I am , that likes to hold my hand and surprize me with a little kiss when I least expect it or give me a wink from across the room just to let me know he is thinking about me or give me a call just to let me know he is thinking about me… Because I will be doing the same..
